    <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-brazil-blue leading-tight mb-6">
      <span data-lang-content="en">Top 5 Ways to Send Money from Brazil in 2026</span>
      <span data-lang-content="zh">2026年从巴西汇款的5大方式</span>
      <span data-lang-content="pt">As 5 Melhores Formas de Enviar Dinheiro do Brasil em 2026</span>
    </h1>

    <img
